  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your color changing staff to solve challenging puzzles. Carry the lessons you learn from each puzzle throughout the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore The World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas of the hub world and  gain access to new puzzle mechanics! You'll learn to use the color changers, teleporters, circuits and more. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chat With Locals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/ab40d1d7804840eedacc524435d5f90a.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/ab40d1d7804840eedacc524435d5f90a.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/ab40d1d7804840eedacc524435d5f90a.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some inhabitants want to help you solve the puzzles! Some would rather you left the puzzles alone. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Undo Your Mistakes, Control Time</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/863269529cc0610b29042ceb92cd90ec.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/863269529cc0610b29042ceb92cd90ec.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/863269529cc0610b29042ceb92cd90ec.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can undo any mistake with the press of a button, and you can rewind, pause, or fast-forward time to suit your needs. Way of Rhea has hard puzzles, but forgiving mechanics--no combat or platforming challenges here.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >End Game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/dcef05aaf07cc95bfb80c1c32d1813d2.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/dcef05aaf07cc95bfb80c1c32d1813d2.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/dcef05aaf07cc95bfb80c1c32d1813d2.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty builds over  time. Use everything you've learned to beat the challenging end game!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play On Steam Deck!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/a7f35cef30ba15f31665b4ff4ee30acc.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I test every build on Steam Deck!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Aspect Ratios</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is currently letter-boxed on non 16:9 aspect ratio monitors. It's tricky to get this right for a 2D game--if we just allow arbitrary aspect ratios, then the camera will point outside the level bounds, or reveal secrets or puzzle elements you're not supposed to see yet. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I'm not super happy about that. If the game does well enough I may be able to create a patch down the line where I do a pass over each puzzle and make custom camera frames for a few more common aspect ratios, but I can't make any promises right now! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join My Discord</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have feedback or just need a hint, the quickest way to reach me is our Discord, linked in the post on the forums.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Future games and beta testing opportunities are announced there, and it's a great place to chat with other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Mason</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Solve Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/4851b84c983bd5ff21cd18f08a47780e.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your color changing staff to solve challenging puzzles. Carry the lessons you learn from each puzzle throughout the game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore The World</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.poster.avif?t=1762594579\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.webm?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/b1dad9dde0e4475fda43cf16f1f6eb80.mp4?t=1762594579\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new areas of the hub world and  gain access to new puzzle mechanics! You'll learn to use the color changers, teleporters, circuits and more. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chat With Locals</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1110620/extras/ab40d1d7804840ee